data.description: Why rent when you can own? Zoned LAR2, situated on a generous 9,040sqft lot located near shops, restaurants, freeways, DTLA and more. Each unit includes inside laundry, assigned parking, gas and electric meter, cooper plumbing throughout and new roofs. The owner is responsible for water only making this a positive cash flowing property.  **VA loan of approximately $721,000 with a very attractive fixed rate and below market of 2.25% interest-only is assumable upon another Veteran approved buyer** All units are tenant occupied, month to month, and paying on time. Whether you're seeking an investment property or a place to call home this exceptional property offers the perfect blend of potential and charm!
